One munhu yoyose hadaha kuhonyigwa kuwa kanoga haulongozi ha Mulungu kwa kutenda Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa, vinoga. Maandiko Yelile yolonga, "Munhu yoyomulonda Mulungu kezakuwa ngima kwa kumuhuwila Mulungu."
