Habule munhu yelihi Mulungu yoyawakalile kowihila kwa miyaka malongo mane? Vino siyo wanhu waja watendile uhasanyi, na wanhu wawo wadanganika kudibwilingu?
Wawo ni welihi Mulungu yoyailahile kuwa, "Hapeni wengile muna ulekezi wake kaidi?" Mbali waja muhala wowalemile kumuhulika Mulungu ni waja muhala?
Ivo chowona kuwa hawadahile kwingila muna dileme kwaviya wakala wabule uhuwilo.
