Wawo ni wawo wowakalile hawahulika Mulungu baho chipindi chiya Mulungu viyakalile yowagozela kwa uhuwilo wake, siku ziya Nuhu viyakalile yang'hali kohumba ngalawa. Wanhu wadodo wawo, ni wanhu wanane muhala wowakomboligwe muna dilamba.
Maabaho mazi yayo yalinga fana viya viya ubatizo uwo womkombola mweye iviya sambi, siwo kufosela wihi wa lukuli lwako, mbali ni lagano kwa Mulungu da kuwa na moyo unogile kufosela kuzilibuka kwa Yesu Chilisito.
